commit.message:
Hotfix Round 2 v2: HOTFIX B(full)+G+H for Order Plan

HOTFIX B (complete): sort crisisItems (Immediate Action) ascending too
HOTFIX G: Order Plan — rows sorted by days_until_critical ASC per supplier;
  suppliers sorted by most urgent item first; overdue order-by dates red+icon;
  mandatory+overdue rows get red left border
HOTFIX H: Order Plan badge tiers — PO SENT (blue) / MATCHED (teal) /
  CONFIRMED ✓ (green) / EN ROUTE ✓✓ (green); badge legend at bottom;
  Order.php findActivePO now returns most advanced active order (in_transit>confirmed>matched>planned)
  with order_type + status fields

